.TH "libnvme" 9 "struct libnbft_discovery" "April 2026" "API Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
struct libnbft_discovery \- Discovery Descriptor
.SH SYNOPSIS
struct libnbft_discovery {
.br
.BI "    int index;"
.br
.BI "    struct libnbft_security *security;"
.br
.BI "    struct libnbft_hfi *hfi;"
.br
.BI "    char *uri;"
.br
.BI "    char *nqn;"
.br
.BI "
};
.br

.SH Members
.IP "index" 12
The number of this Discovery Descriptor in the Discovery
Descriptor List.
.IP "security" 12
The Security Profile Descriptor, see \fIstruct libnbft_security\fP.
.IP "hfi" 12
The HFI Descriptor associated with this Discovery Descriptor.
See \fIstruct libnbft_hfi\fP.
.IP "uri" 12
A URI which indicates an NVMe Discovery controller associated
with this Discovery Descriptor.
.IP "nqn" 12
An NVMe Discovery controller NQN.
